title: Dodgers and Mattingly part ways in mutual agreement
text:
> Sports Dodgers and Mattingly part ways in mutual agreement Dodger President of Baseball Operations Andrew Friedman, speaks during a news conference in Los Angeles on Thursday, Oct. 22, 2015. Don Mattingly won't return as manager of the Los Angeles Dodgers next year after agreeing with his bosses that he and the team needed a fresh start. (AP Photo/Richard Vogel)
